<div class="meta-title">
<p>助理研究员Picsell Dois的人（马）事档案</p>
</div>
<table style="width: 100%; margin-top: 25px; vertical-align:top;">
<tr style="width: 100%; vertical-align:top;">
<td style="width: 50%; border-right: 2.5px solid #d7d7d7; vertical-align:top;">
<div style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com" target="_blank"><img src="http://scp-equestria.wdfiles.com/local--files/about-the-scp-foundation/SCP_LOGO_CN_GREY757575.png" style="width: 125px" alt="SCP_LOGO_CN_GREY757575.png" class="image" /></a><br />
<span style="font-size:150%;"><br />
<strong><span style="color: #757575">SCP基金会中国分部</span></strong><br /></span>
<p><strong><span style="color: #757575">SCP FOUNDATION</span></strong><br />
<strong><span style="color: #757575">CHINESE BRANCH</span></strong></p>
</div>
